                <td bgcolor="#37437B" valign="top"><font color="white" face="verdana" size="2"><small>Posted&nbsp;-&nbsp;01/24/2004&nbsp;: 5:44:27 PM</small><hr size="1"><span class="spnMessageText"> Well... No need to mem any spells that takes longer than 4 sec to cast... <br /><br />1)<br />Anull magic (anull your opponent to start with , strip him/her completly)<br /><br />2)<br />Saryns Kiss ( keeps you up on hp and a nasty dot on your target)<br /><br />3)<br />Embracing Darkness ( gets resisted alot, but keep spamming. Once it sticks ur opp. is toast! )<br /><br />4)<br />Touch of Mujaki ( spam that spell :) )<br /><br />5)<br />Touch of Death ( keeps your pet alive)<br /><br />6)<br />Shadow step (Dont underestimate this lovely lowlevel spell, zap around :-))<br /><br />7) <br />Have a low level dot up also.. cast it on yourself if your up against a chanter (it breaks mez :-))<br /><br />8)<br />Last slot is for SoS ( Dont want to run out of mana midfight)<br /><br />AA)<br />Wake the dead, Pet lay hands and Lifeburn are also deadly in PvP, if u have them USE em..<br /><br /><br /><br /></span></font></td>
